To Interpret And Evaluate How Migration And Development Are Framed, And Analyse The Implications;
To Critically Reflect On Policy Interventions (Such As The Sustainable Development Goals, “Migration Deals” Etc.) And Interpret Their Assumptions And Impact
To Communicate Their Knowledge, Individually And In Groups, In Different Formats (Oral, Written And Multi-Media).

